===Tennessee Titans===
On August 30, 2014, the [[Tennessee Titans]] traded Edwards to the [[Dallas Cowboys]] for a conditional seventh round pick in the [[2015 NFL Draft]].<ref>{{cite news|work=Tennessean.com|url=http://www.tennessean.com/story/titansinsider/2014/08/30/titans-maikon-bonani-nfl-travis-coons/14864631/|title=Titans cut Maikon Bonani, Moise Fokou; Edwards traded|first=Jim|last=Wyatt|date=August 30, 2014|accessdate=2014-09-20}}</ref>

===Dallas Cowboys===
The [[Dallas Cowboys]] waived Edwards on September 20, 2014.<ref>{{cite web|work=ESPN.com|url=http://espn.go.com/blog/dallas-cowboys/post/_/id/4733925/cowboys-promote-lb-smith-from-practice-squad|title=LB Keith Smith moves up to 53-man roster|date=September 20, 2014|first=Tim|last=MacMahon|accessdate=2014-09-20}}</ref>

